<title>Other Grid functions</title>
<p>
In addition to <pf>draw</pf> and <pf>paint</pf>, the <pf>GridCanvas</pf> class provides functions for working with the grid itself.
<pf>numRows</pf> and <pf>numCols</pf> return the number of rows and columns.
We can get this information from the 2D array, using <pf>length</pf>:
